<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

    <head>
        <title>BLACKBOX</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
        <meta name="description" content="">
        <meta name="author" content="">
        <link href="stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="stylesheets/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:400,300,300italic,400italic,700,700italic,900,900italic" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
        <link href="stylesheets/magnific-popup.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="stylesheets/creative.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>

    <body>
        <nav id="mainNav" class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/" class="navbar-brand js-scroll-trigger">BLACKBOX</a>
                <button type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation" class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div id="navbarResponsive" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <% if(id) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                          <a href="/logout" class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger">logout</a>
                        </li>
                        <% }else{ %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                          <a href="/login" class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger">login</a>
                        </li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a href="/consult" class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger">Consult</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a href="/eyewitness" class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger">Eyewitness</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a href="/setting" class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger">Setting</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                          <a class="nav-link js-scroll-trigger" href="/admin"><i class="fa fa-1g fa-id-badge text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i></a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <header class="masthead text-center text-white d-flex">
            <div class="container my-auto">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
                        <h1 class="text-uppercase">
                            <strong>LEGAL ADVISORY SERVICE</strong>
                        </h1>
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
                        <p class="text-faded mb-5">블랙박스 영상을 의뢰하여
                            <br>전문 변호사가 교통사고 과실에 관하여
                            <br>법률적으로 자문하는 서비스를 제공합니다.</p>
		<% if (!id) {%>
                        <a href="/choice" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger">Make Account</a>
		<% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>
        <section id="contact">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
                        <h2 class="section-heading">Let's Get In Touch!</h2>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p class="mb-5">문의하시고 싶은 내용이 있으시면 메일을 보내주시면 연락해드리겠습니다!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 ml-auto text-center">
                        <i class="fa fa-phone fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact"></i>
                        <p>123-456-6789</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 mr-auto text-center">
                        <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact"></i>
                        <p>
                            <a href="mailto:your-email@your-domain.com">blackbox@gmail.com</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <script src="javascripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="javascripts/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <script src="javascripts/jquery.easing.min.js"></script>
        <script src="javascripts/scrollreveal.min.js"></script>
        <script src="javascripts/jquery.magnific-popup.min.js"></script>
        <script src="javascripts/creative.min.js"></script>
    </body>

</html>
